author: @DevlinTay
content: It likely brought in economic value to Rio and Brazil that is well over the 12 million she was paid (if she was indeed paid) due to the multiplier effect of 1.6 million people coming into Rio and spending money on hotel accommodation, food, merchandise, and everything else - a bonanza for local businesses, local workers and the local economy as a whole. So why complain?
